!IMPORTANT! You need UHD version 3.9.7 in order to compile and run this program.
            Be sure to install and link this specific version before proceeding.

Build the program using CMake:

    $ mkdir build
    $ cd build
    $ cmake ..
    $ make

To launch the system, attach the USRP B210 to the host and run:

    $ ./btsniffer 

To see all available options, run:

    $ ./btsniffer --help

